ey wish\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/05/explained-netflix-review-vox-documentary-show-1201967788/|title='Explained' Review: Netflix's Intriguing Docuseries Tackles Every Topic in the World, From K-Pop to DNA, in 20 Minute Chunks|last=Greene|first=Steve|date=2018-05-24|website=IndieWire|language=en|access-date=2018-12-20}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|https://www.netflix.com/title/80216752|name=''Explained''}} on [[Netflix]]\n* {{IMDb title|8005374}}\n\n{{Netflix original current series}}\n{{Vox Media}}\n[[Category:2018 American television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2010s American documentary television series]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Netflix original documentary television series]]\n[[Category:Vox Media]]\n", "name_user": "Jayab314", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Explained_(TV_series)"}
